{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2020/02/project-askent-admin-audience-client/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"325aee4d-8f30-58df-bb66-4a5a602405f0","html":"<!-- endExcerpt -->\n<p>武汉新冠状病毒肆掠，春节在家待着，休息期间继续给<a href=\"/2019/12/create-presentation-tool-from-scratch\">之前立的项目 Askent</a> 添砖加瓦，目前实现增删活动、观众端提问、审核编辑提问、提问增删改实时同步。还差展示大屏端功能，现有功能也只是实现了雏形，working in progress…</p>\n<p>项目是模仿 <a href=\"https://sli.do/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Sli.do</a> 做的，随着功能开发深入研究后，\n越发觉得这是一款<a href=\"https://blog.sli.do/slido-brand-refresh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">精心设计和开发</a>的产品👍。</p>\n<p>Repository: <a href=\"https://github.com/BerlinChan/askent\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/BerlinChan/askent</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"screenshots\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#screenshots\" aria-label=\"screenshots permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Screenshots</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/abe63fa74866555862ff3bafb544e0b2/7b58d/askent-admin.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.36842105263158%; position: relativ