n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/7b58d/askent-audience-event.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.36842105263158%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/5ed05/askent-audience-event.webp 190w,\n/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/9d76b/askent-audience-event.webp 380w,\n/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/33466/askent-audience-event.webp 760w,\n/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/ca244/askent-audience-event.webp 1140w,\n/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/e9f1f/askent-audience-event.webp 1200w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/253c6/askent-audience-event.png 190w,\n/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/810ee/askent-audience-event.png 380w,\n/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/b4918/askent-audience-event.png 760w,\n/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/c0204/askent-audience-event.png 1140w,\n/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/7b58d/askent-audience-event.png 1200w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f7e218d42828f6d15e8e93788475e8f6/b4918/askent-audience-event.png\"\n            alt=\"Askent-audience-event screen\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<center>观众端提问与投票</center>\n<h2 id=\"tech-stack\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tech-stack\" aria-label=\"tech stack permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tech-stack</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Typescript</li>\n<li>GraphQL</li>\n<li>Apollo</li>\n<li>Prisma2</li>\n<li>Nexus</li>\n<li>React</li>\n<li>MaterialUI</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Askent 也是我的一个技术探索实践项目，所以技术选型偏激进，\n特别是还在 preview 版本的 <a href=\"https://github.com/prisma/prisma2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Prisma2</a>，\n很多 <a href=\"https://github.com/prisma/prisma-client-js/issues/5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">aggregation 查询</a>都还未实现，\n且存在严重 bug，但活跃的社区应该能逐渐完善它。\n我也借此以一位深入使用者的身份，旁观一个开源项目的发展。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.apollographql.com/docs/react/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code class=\"language-text\">Apollo-Client</code></a> + <a href=\"https://www.apollographql.com/docs/apollo-server/data/subscriptions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code class=\"language-text\">Subscription</code></a> 是消息实时同步的绝佳使用场景，来开发提问的多端实时同步非常方便。\n它实质是 WebSockets 的 API 高级封装，在<a href=\"https://www.apollographql.com/docs/react/data/subscriptions/#authentication-over-websocket\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">授权</a>、<a href=\"https://www.apollographql.com/docs/apollo-server/data/subscriptions/#subscription-filters\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">订阅过滤</a>方面使用更加方便。</p>","excerpt":"","fields":{"slug":"/2020/02/project-askent-admin-audience-client","categorySlugs":["/category/前端/"],"tagSlugs":["/tag/askent/","/tag/个人项目/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"互动演示工具 Askent 已开发出管理与观众端雏形","date":"2020-02-05T10:46:37.121Z","categories":["前端"],"description":"武汉新冠状病毒肆掠，春节在家待着，休息期间继续给之前立的项目 Askent 添砖加瓦，目前实现增删活动、观众端提问、审核编辑提问、提问增删改实时同步。还差展示大屏端功能……","tags":["Askent","个人项目"],"slug":"/2020/02/project-askent-admin-audience-client","featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/3c5eff599f0bc039b46fe4c34309ce4f/ed3fb/askent-admin-event.png","srcSet":"/static/3c5eff599f0bc039b46fe4c34309ce4f/ed3fb/askent-admin-event.png 800w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/3c5eff599f0bc039b46fe4c34309ce4f/e7773/askent-admin-event.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}}}},"prevPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019/12/create-presentation-tool-from-scratch"},"frontmatter":{"title":"从零开始，创建一个多端互动演示工具"}},"nextPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/02/logout-weibo"},"frontmatter":{"title":"销户微博账号"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020/02/project-askent-admin-audience-client","prevPostSlug":"/2019/12/create-presentation-tool-from-scratch","nextPostSlug":"/2020/02/logout-weibo"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2727970573","3709504828","4110059069"],"slicesMap":{}}